				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Stealing Guard's Kills with Charm<a name="16378"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 20 04 7:56 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Hey I am so proud, I was reading about all those strategies found a while even before I started to play and was thinking that everything had been done aleady, but here is a strategy I never saw before, working and funny <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> 
<br />

<br />
So I am doing it in Echo Cavern, level 27 with my new charming song, when Soloing. I pull a mob, take it to the guard, let the guard beat the crap out of him, then charm the mob, go a bit far away and kill the mob. I was told this didn't work with players beating the crap but at least it is working with the guard. 
<br />

<br />
Note: when I pull two mobs I charm one to beat the other one but this is standard. And don t forget to slow the mob when he is almost beaten: otherwise chances he will go away right on the guard and you won't get the XP.
<br />

<br />
++
<br />
<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /> 
<br />
Clarine TonneaudeBiere, from Karana</span></td>
